cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NGU to the same IP as GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF will cause IP address conflict and prevent NG-U interface establishment.
cu.explanation_zh: 將 GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NGU 設定為與 GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF 相同的 IP 會導致 IP 地址衝突，並阻止 NG-U 接口建立。

du.explanation_en: Setting remote_n_address to the same IP as local_n_address will cause F1 interface loopback and prevent proper DU-CU communication.
du.explanation_zh: 將 remote_n_address 設定為與 local_n_address 相同的 IP 會導致 F1 接口迴路，並阻止正確的 DU-CU 通信。
